    "lyrics": {
      "text": "O_ all-laud-ed Mar-tyrs of the Lord, lo, the earth con-cealed you not; but ra-ther Heav-en re-ceived you and the gates of Par-a-dise wel-comed you and o-pened. And as ye now dwell there-in ye joy-ful-ly par-take of the Tree of Life. Thus, in-ter-cede, we pray, with the Mas-ter,__ e-ven Christ the Lord, that He grant peace and great mer-cy to__ our__ souls."
